ic device has a Bluetooth connection, ArcX will work with all of them.  <\/p>"}},"166442457738b23caf-2":{"type":"item","settings":{"title":"What size ArcX should I order?","content":"<p>There is no need to worry about sizing. We will ship five different sized outer rings in each box. <\/p><p>The rings have the following internal diameters:<\/p><ul><li>16mm (0.62) <\/li><li>18mm (0.70 in)<\/li><li>20mm (0.78 in)<\/li><li>22mm (0.86 in) <\/li><li>24mm (0.94 in)<\/li><\/ul><p>Find the right size for you and insert the tech module. It’s that easy. <strong>Each ring will stretch up to 20% <\/strong>so if worn on a naked finger the same ring can be stretched to wear on a gloved finger if required.<\/p>"}},"4bbe41ed-fe37-40a6-841f-a54cd7db45a4":{"type":"item","settings":{"title":"Does ArcX come with a warranty?","content":"<p><strong>ArcX comes with a one year warranty.<\/strong> Our manufacturing partner is one of the leading global electronics manufacturers and each ArcX is comprehensively tested before leaving the factory. In the unlikely event that your ArcX stops working, we will replace it.<\/p>"}},"1b67610d-10dc-45ce-a4c6-1d8d78baac5a":{"type":"item","settings":{"title":"What if I’m not happy with my ArcX?","content":"<p>We’re sure you’ll love your ArcX but if for any reason you're unhappy with our product or you just change your mind simply return your unit within 30 days, undamaged with the original packaging and we’ll refund you, no questions asked.<\/p>"}}},"block_order":["166442457738b23caf-0","166442457738b23caf-1","166442457738b23caf-2","4bbe41ed-fe37-40a6-841f-a54cd7db45a4","1b67610d-10dc-45ce-a4c6-1d8d78baac5a"],"settings":{"full_width":false,"subheading":"","title":"Have a question? We're here to help.","content":"","team_avatar_width":160,"support_hours":"Our customer support is available Monday to Friday: 8am-8pm.","answer_time":"Average answer time: 24h","button_text":"","button_url":"","text_position":"start","background":"#242424","background_gradient